name: Mycouncil
0:
”Alexa open my council”
”What day are the bins collected”

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my council
des: This is a bot to find out about rubbish and recycle collections in the UK. You can ask about blue, black, and green bins to find when the next collection day will be.
